properties.name: Pass Participle
properties.description:
There are some hills that are fun to do and some that are fun to have done, if you know what we mean. At this point, we've explored just about every pass over our nearby hills/mountains. Just about, but not every. This week we set about to find a new one  and find one we did. But we didn't find time to, you know, scout it. So come tonight and we will discover together how to properly phrase our enjoyment thereof!

(Only realized after the fact that we'd actually had a ride with a very similar theme before. But this is indeed a totally different, unrelated route.)
